turn all the way around go forward make right go forward toward fridge
open fridge door put wine on bottom shelf close fridge door
open fridge door pick up wine bottle close door make right go forward make right again walk to wall make left to face table

high_descs: Go to the counter in front of you.
Pick up the wine bottle at the end of the counter.
Go to the fridge behind you.
Chill the wine bottle in the fridge.
Go to the table to your right.
Place the wine bottle in front of the other wine bottle.
anns.task_desc: Place chilled wine on the table.

high_descs: Walk forward four steps then turn left and walk so you stand facing the wine bottle on the counter.
Pick up the wine bottle off of the counter.
Turn around and walk over to the fridge so you are facing it.
Open the fridge and place the wine bottle on the bottom shelf to the left and then close the fridge and let it chill for a bit before opening the fridge and retrieving it then close the fridge.
Turn right and walk until the counter on the left side of you ends then turn right and walk to the wall then turn left so you are facing the table.
Place the wine bottle so it's under the other wine bottle but slightly to the right.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold bottle of wine on the table.
